title: Ep.8: Packers Power Rank, Steelers Playoff Hopes, Derrick Henry, Music and more.
description: Today we asked ourselves if the Packers are the best team in the NFL, do the steelers still have a shot in the playoffs, and what do the Titans have to do to win games without their star RB. We dive a little bit into the music industry and GOAT debates also.
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
